                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Tower</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Embassy of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Berlin</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-01-02">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 2, 1903</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Tower acknowledges the receipt of the Department’s telegrams conveying the
                    answer of Venezuela and relating to Mr. Bowen, which he has communicated to the
                    German Government.)</p>
